_:N11714b10ec1b4cb98813fcdcf7e263b1 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>John Black has worked for LGC since 2008 and joined the Government Chemist programme in 2020. John also manages the Chemical &amp; Biological Metrology programme, delivered as part of the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/national-measurement-system/uk-national-measurement-system\">UK National Measurement System (NMS)</a>.</p>\n" .
